de.axelwernicke.mypod.util
Class ClipsTableUtils

java.lang.Object
  de.axelwernicke.mypod.util.ClipsTableUtils
public class ClipsTableUtils
extends java.lang.Object

This class defines some helpers for the list view table. For each mp3 meta data an abstract name and a number are defined. Furthermore a name for each column of the list view table is defined.

Author:
axel wernicke
